/p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn10"></a><a href="#_ednref10">[10]</a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">Myanmar Const. at Ch. XIV, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">445; Ch. 1, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">20(b), Ch. VII, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> 343.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn11"></a><a href="#_ednref11">[11]</a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">Myanmar Const. at Ch. III, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">71(b), Ch. IV, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">141(b).</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn12"></a><a href="#_ednref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> Myanmar Const. at </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn13"></a><a href="#_ednref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> Myanmar Constitution, </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">at .</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn14"></a><a href="#_ednref14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">Myanmar Constitution at Ch. 1, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">20(b), Ch. VII, art.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> 343.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn15"></a><a href="#_ednref15">[15]</a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt"> International Parliamentary Union, </span><span style=