itment-to-End-Sexual-Violence-in-Conflict"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.scribd.com/doc/170678527/A-Declaration-of-Commitment-to-End-Sexual-Violence-in-Conflict</span></a><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">November</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic"> 2013</span></p></body></html>